5.0.3.0

- Added tuned support for 29 more headsets and headphones, bringing Lucid to 70 enabled models.
- New additions range from gaming headsets like the Astro A50 Gen 5, SteelSeries Nova 3 and Nova 7 Gen 2 to headphones like the FiiO FT1, HD 800 S, Sundara, LCD-X, and Porta Pro.
- Fixed correction generation for devices whose left and right measurements use different frequency grids.
- Astro A50 Gen 5 now has its own tuning and can be identified automatically from its base station.
